Freddy Silva is with us
today to tie together

00:00:49.980 --> 00:00:53.395 align:middle line:84%
Andean temples and those of
Egypt, which this is a new one.

00:00:53.395 --> 00:00:54.520 align:middle line:90%
>>FREDDY SILVA: Absolutely.

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:54.920 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:56.630 align:middle line:10%
But before we go
into the new one,

00:00:56.630 --> 00:00:58.190 align:middle line:10%
