00:01:02.536 --> 00:01:04.910 align:middle line:84%
you were saying
what's so fascinating

00:01:04.910 --> 00:01:09.740 align:middle line:84%
about the ancient information
that's emerging today

00:01:09.740 --> 00:01:12.590 align:middle line:84%
is exactly these
things, the ties

00:01:12.590 --> 00:01:15.290 align:middle line:84%
between places that are so
disparate geographically

00:01:15.290 --> 00:01:16.610 align:middle line:90%
and culturally.

00:01:16.610 --> 00:01:19.340 align:middle line:84%
And you said, oh, well let
me tell you about this.

